data.description: 2001 Manufactured home (appx. 1,400 square feet) on a permanent foundation.  (VA and FHA) ok.  Fenced. 3 bedroom, 2 full bathrooms.  Garden tub with separate shower.  Living room with fire place.  Open floor plan to dining area.  Utility (laundry) room just off the kitchen with washer and dryer hook-ups.  All electric power, septic system and sand point well.  New roof installed in 2023.
